      "repair_reason": "Manual maintainer review is required because the PR is draft/protected, security-sensitive, asks product/API boundary questions, and still has blocking findings plus proof gaps.; Needs attention: The diff adds security-sensitive policy guardrails, but the advertised doctor guardrail path is not activated and malformed deny rules are not deterministically rejected.; Review finding: [P1] Load policy checks in doctor l... (sha=56ea512ebda07067d5e8ef530b2c1400bd13e93b)",
